00:01:39.780 --> 00:01:45.680
So today I thought we would talk about comics.
I'm gonna talk about what are comics?

00:01:45.680 --> 00:01:49.710
[pause - writing on board]

00:01:49.710 --> 00:01:50.710
And where do they come from?

00:01:50.710 --> 00:01:51.710
[pause - writing on board]

00:01:51.710 --> 00:01:52.710
Where do they come from?

00:01:52.710 --> 00:01:58.900
I'm just more comfortable with a marker in
my hand.

00:01:58.900 --> 00:01:59.900
[pause - writing on board]

00:01:59.900 --> 00:02:06.120
And then I'll do a little bit of history of
why I do comics and the comics I've done specifically

00:02:06.120 --> 00:02:07.120
 -

00:02:07.120 --> 00:02:08.120
[pause - writing on board]

