00:02:16.940 --> 00:02:19.400
So what are comics?
Anybody?

00:02:19.400 --> 00:02:21.169
What is a comic?
Someone define comic for me.

00:02:21.169 --> 00:02:22.169
[pause]

00:02:22.169 --> 00:02:25.310
By the way if you're not here this room is
completely packed.

00:02:25.310 --> 00:02:26.310
[laughter]

00:02:26.310 --> 00:02:29.779
&gt;&gt;voice in audience: It's a very, very short
